{"tid":853292,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓價回調】屯門利寶大廈叫價308萬 代理：業主怕後市大跌出貨","createTime":"2018-10-08T13:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T04:33:31.000Z","uid":83582,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"4a77a5e4a912407650fe90a87d03586035dd37f2","tid":853292,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"12:15 2018/10/08<br />\n<br />\n加息等樓市負面因素影響，有二、三綫上車屋苑價錢急速回落，當中屯門知名的單幢樓、位於青河坊3號的利寶大廈，有投資者劈價求沽，叫價低見308萬元。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，利寶大廈一個實用面積234平方呎低層單位，新近減價至308萬元放售，每呎叫價13,162元。區內代理稱，單位業主屬於投資者，因為怕後市大跌，所以減價出貨。<br />\n<br />\n翻查成交，234平方呎的同室單高數層單位，今年4月造價要333萬；同樣4月一個中層同室單位造價為335萬元。再追溯之前的話，則要追到去年11月，同室中高層單位以303.8萬元易手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2175000/2177718/ckfn20161101004_09_1024x1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2175000%2F2177718%2Fckfn20161101004_09_1024x1024_1024.jpg&h=e8becbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源: 地產站 (香港經濟日報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2177718/%E3%80%90%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF%E3%80%91%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%88%A9%E5%AF%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E5%8F%AB%E5%83%B9308%E8%90%AC%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%EF%BC%9A%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E6%80%95%E5%BE%8C%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%A8?mtc=60007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2177718%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%2583%25B9308%25E8%2590%25AC%2520%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2580%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A8%3Fmtc%3D60007&d=agOrf3GLl%2FQ9LcKIXunTodr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bc7dbb84\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2177718/%E